<ul>
    <li><strong>Pillar 1 - Prevention Architecture:</strong> Building Tier 1 and Tier 2 systems that catch problems before they become crises.</li>
    <li><strong>Pillar 2 - Capacity Building:</strong> Training staff to handle most situations independently so you can focus on complex cases.</li>
    <li><strong>Pillar 3 - Strategic Communication:</strong> Teaching admin and stakeholders the value of proactive support so they become allies, not obstacles.</li>
    <li><strong>Pillar 4 - Sustainable Boundaries:</strong> Creating clear protocols that protect your time and energy without guilt.</li>
    <li><strong>Pillar 5 - Continuous Improvement:</strong> Using data to refine your systems and demonstrate your impact.</li>
</ul>
